Enum Class RoadEnum

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<RoadEnum>
Traffic.RoadEnum
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<RoadEnum>, Constable
public enum RoadEnum extends Enum<RoadEnum>
Enumeration representing all roads available in the system. Each road connects two nodes.
